  "remarks": "TAi.108 Title: Maulavi. Designation: Governor of Uruzgan Province under the Taliban regime. Reportedly deceased in North Afghanistan in 1999. Belonged to Wardak tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 27 Jul. 2010; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 February 2001 (amended on 3 Sep. 2003, 21 Sep 2007, 24 Mar. 2009, 29 Nov. 2011, 18 May 2012)",
